---
title: Double Moroccan Chicken & Coconut Stew with Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: This fragrant stew gets its flavour from the delicious Moroccan-inspired curry paste. A mild yet tasty base of onion and coconut milk is revived with refreshing herbs, all on a bed of pillowy garlic rice. Divine!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-chicken-coconut-stew-1d4a27d4.jpg
